     [Show layouts comparison]
    
    > Now that the projects are open, both in Lens Studio and in Unity let’s translate Lens Studio into Unity language. 
    
    > From Unity to Lens Studio
    
    Hierarchy, Scene, Inspector - same across both tools 
    
    Game > Preview
    Project > Asset Browser 
    Console > Logger 

